<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>Did you requested a link to change your password? Here is! 
  You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email and check your security.</p>
<p>Your password will not change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
